data.description: Welcome to your new home in the vibrant Vermont-Slauson neighborhood of Los Angeles! This captivating corner lot gem has just received a significant price reduction of over $9k, making it an irresistible opportunity to claim your piece of prime real estate.With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this home offers the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Inside discover modern amenities including a newer AC system and a comprehensive security setup with indoor and outdoor cameras, ensuring your peace of mind.The allure doesn't stop indoors. Step outside into your own private retreat, complete with a charming backyard featuring a retractable awning and rain collection barrels, perfect for those cozy evenings or entertaining friends and family. Plus, the detached garage comes with an EV charger, catering to your eco-friendly lifestyle.Conveniently located near USC and Sofi Stadium, this property puts you at the heart of it all, with easy access to local amenities, dining, and entertainment options.
